                 How to use
 =====================================
 
 === In your config ===
<pre>
        'modules'=>array(
                'login',
        ),

        'components'=>array(
                'user'=>array(
                        'allowAutoLogin'=>true,
                        'loginUrl'=>array('/login/default/index'),
                ),
        ),

</pre>
                === or you can use
                        'loginUrl'=>array('login'),
                ===

=== To create DB table ===

http://yoursite.com/login/default/easyinstall


=== For logout you can use ===

array('/login/default/logout')

